<h3>Setup Time: Amateur</h3>
<p>Hunters on the "Amateur" difficulty have five minutes (300 seconds) setup time before ghosts can hunt.</p>
<div class="timer" id="setup-amateur-timer" data-duration="300">
    <p class="heading">Setup: Amateur</p>
    <p class="time"></p>
    <button type="button" class="start-btn">Start</button>
    <button type="button" class="reset-btn">Reset</button>
</div>
<h3>Setup Time: Intermediate</h3>
<p>Hunters on the "Intermediate" difficulty have two minutes (120 seconds) setup time before ghosts can hunt.</p>
<div class="timer" id="setup-intermediate-timer" data-duration="120">
    <p class="heading">Setup: Intermediate</p>
    <p class="time"></p>
    <button type="button" class="start-btn">Start</button>
    <button type="button" class="reset-btn">Reset</button>
</div>
<h3>Hunt Cooldown</h3>
<p>Once a hunt ends, a ghost must wait at least 25 seconds before attempting to hunt again.</p>
<div class="timer" id="hunt-cooldown-timer" data-duration="25">
    <p class="heading">Hunt Cooldown</p>
    <p class="time"></p>
    <button type="button" class="start-btn">Start</button>
    <button type="button" class="reset-btn">Reset</button>
</div>
<h3>Incensed Spirit</h3>
<p>Using incense near a <ghost-link name="Spirit"></ghost-link> will prevent it from hunting for three minutes (180 seconds).</p>
<div class="timer" id="spirit-incense-timer" data-duration="180">
    <p class="heading">Incensed Spirit</p>
    <p class="time"></p>
    <button type="button" class="start-btn">Start</button>
    <button type="button" class="reset-btn">Reset</button>
</div>
</timers>

